rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Unconstrained properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators without specific or implicit restrictions to RDA entities.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abbreviatedTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abbreviated title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title that has been abbreviated for purposes of indexing or identification.
rdf:Description.reg:name: forkortetTitel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har forkortet titel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en titel, der er forkortet mhp. indeksering eller identifikation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridged as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that shortens a source resource without changing a general meaning or manner of presentation.
rdf:Description.reg:name: forkortetTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er forkortet til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der forkorter en oprindelig ressource uden at ændre den overordnede betydning eller præsentationsmåde.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgementOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridgement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been abridged, i.e., shortened without changing a general meaning or manner of presentation of a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: forkortelseAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er forkortelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet forkortet, dvs. afkortet, uden at der er ændret på en oprindelig ressources overordnede betydning eller præsentationsmåde.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abridger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by shortening or condensing an original resource but leaving the nature and content substantially unchanged.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Substantial modification that results in the creation of a new resource is excluded.
rdf:Description.reg:name: forkorter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har forkorter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at forkorte eller komprimere en originalressource, men som i alt væsentligt har ladt originalens karakter og indhold uændret.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Væsentlige ændringer, der resulterer i skabelsen af en ny ressource, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridger of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by shortening or condensing an original resource but leaving the nature and content substantially unchanged to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: forkorterAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er forkorter af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at forkorte eller komprimere den oprindelige ressource, men som i alt væsentligt har ladt den oprindelige ressources karakter og indhold være uændret til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has absorbed agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent that was absorbed by another agent.
rdf:Description.reg:name: absorberetAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har absorberet agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en agent, der var absorberet af en anden agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that incorporates another resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: indlemmetAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indlemmet af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der inkorporerer en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedInPartBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that incorporates part of the content of another resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: delvisIndlemmetAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis indlemmet af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der delvis inkorporerer en anden ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbingAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has absorbing agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an agent that absorbed another agent.
rdf:Description.reg:name: indlemmendeAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indlemmende agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en agent, der indlemmede en anden agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionInPartOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been partially incorporated into another resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: delvisAbsorberingAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis absorbering af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er delvis inkorporeret i en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been incorporated into another resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: absorberingAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er absorbering af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet inkorporeret i en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that abbreviates a source resource in a brief, objective manner.
rdf:Description.reg:name: sammenfattetSom
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfattet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der forkorter en oprindelig ressource på en kortfattet, objektiv måde.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an abstracting and indexing service that abstracts the contents of a source entity.
rdf:Description.reg:name: sammenfattetI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfattet i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en abstracts- og indekseringsservice, der sammenfatter en oprindelig kildes indehold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been abstracted, i.e., abbreviated in a brief, objective manner.
rdf:Description.reg:name: sammenfatningAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfatning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er sammenfattet, dvs. forkortet på en kortfattet, objektiv måde.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractsFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracts for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose contents have been abstracted by an abstracting and indexing service.
rdf:Description.reg:name: sammenfatningerAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammenfatninger af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvis indhold er blevet sammenfattet af en abstract- og indekseringsservice.

rdf:Description.reg:name: academicDegree
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has academic degree
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a rank conferred as a guarantee of academic proficiency.
rdf:Description.reg:name: akademiskGrad
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har akademisk grad
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en rang, der tildeles som garanti for akademisk færdighed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accessibilityContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accessibility content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of content that provides alternative sensory modes to perceive a primary content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Accessibility content includes accessible labels, audio description, captioning, image description, sign language, and subtitles. Accessibility content does not include subtitles in a language different from the spoken content.
rdf:Description.reg:name: tilgængelighedsfremmendeIndhold
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har tilgængelighedsfremmende indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en indikation af indhold, der giver alternative sansemåder for at forstå en ressources primære indhold.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Omfatter lydbeskrivelser, rubrikker, billedbeskrivelser, tegnsprog, og undertekster. Omfatter ikke undertekster på et andet sprog end det talte.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompaniedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is accompanied by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource issued with another resource, without any relationship to its content.
rdf:Description.reg:name: ledsagetAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er ledsaget af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource udgivet sammen med en anden ressource uden nogen relation til dens indhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompanyingResourceRelationshipWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accompanying resource relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an augmentation of, or is augmented by, or is complemented by, or accompanies, or is accompanied by a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: ledsagetRessourcerelationMed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ledsaget ressource-relation med
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er en berigelse af, eller er beriget af, eller er komplementeret af en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has actor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: skuespiller
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har skuespiller
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en performer, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at fungere som rolleindehaver eller aktør i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is actor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: skuespillerI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er skuespiller i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver, der bidrager til en ressource ved at være skuespiller eller musiker i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been modified for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies to changes in form or to resources completely rewritten in the same form.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdelseAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet ændret til et andet formål, en anden brug eller et andet medium end det, det oprindeligt var beregnet til.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Gælder for ændringer i form eller for ressourcer, der er omskrevet fuldstændigt i samme form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that modifies a source resource for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies to changes in form or to resources completely rewritten in the same form.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetSom
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der modificerer en oprindelig ressource til et andet formål, en anden brug eller et andet medium end det, det oprindeligt var beregnet til.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation gælder for ændringer i form eller for ressourcer, der er omskrevet fuldstændigt i samme form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPicture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a motion picture based on the source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetSomFilm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en film baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPictureScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a motion picture, based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetSomFilm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af en drejebog til en film, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a radio program based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilRadioprogram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til radioprogram (udtryk)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et radioprogram baseret på et oprindeligt udtryk.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioScript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a script for a radio program, based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilRadiomanuskript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til radiomanuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til et radioprogram, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a television program based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilTvprogram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til tv-program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et TV-program baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a television program, based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilTvmanuskript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til tv-manuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til et tv-program, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a video based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilVideo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en video baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideoScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a video, based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilVideomanuskript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til videomanuskript
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til en video, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsChoreography
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as choreography
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of movement based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilKoreografi
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til koreografi
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af bevægelse baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsGraphicNovel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as graphic novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a graphic novel based on a source resource
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilGraphicNovel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til graphic novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en graphic novel baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsLibretto
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a text of an opera or other resource for a musical stage, or an oratorio, based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilLibretto
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af tekst til en opera eller en anden ressource for den musikalske scene eller et oratorium baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsMusicalTheatre
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as musical theatre
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical theatre resource based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilMusikteater
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til musikteater
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en musikteater-ressource baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsOpera
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as opera
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an opera based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilOpera
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til opera
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en opera baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsOratorio
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as oratorio
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an oratorio based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetTilOratoriumVærk
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet til oratorium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et oratorium baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of a screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video, based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetSomDrejebog
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som drejebog
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et manuskript til en film, et tv-program eller en video, baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsVideoGame
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video game
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to relates a resource to a video game based on a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetSomComputerspil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbejdet som computerspil
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en videospilsressource baseret på en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedInVerseAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted in verse as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a literary composition in verse form adapted from a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdetIVersformSom
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: bearbejdet i versform som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en litterær komposition i versform, bearbejdet ud fra en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addenda
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of brief content that is essential for the completeness of another resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: tillæg
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er tillæg
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af kortfattet indhold, som er væsentligt for fuldstændigheden af en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addendaTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is completed with brief content from another resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: tillægTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er tillæg til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvortil der er tilføjet kortfattet ekstra materiale fra en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: additionalScaleInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has additional scale information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an indication of supplemental information about scale.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Statement of comparative measurements or limitation of the scale to particular parts of the content of a resource are included.
rdf:Description.reg:name: supplerendeMålestoksforhold
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har supplerende målestoksforhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en indikation af supplerende oplysninger om målestoksforhold.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Supplerende målestoksforhold omfatter angivelse i flere måleenheder eller som begrænsning af målestoksforholdet til visse dele af ressourcen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has addressee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent to whom a resource or part of a resource is addressed.
rdf:Description.reg:name: adressat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har adressat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, som en ressource eller en del af en ressource er adresseret til.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addresseeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addressee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to whom a resource or part of a resource is addressed to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: adressatI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er adressat i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, som en ressource eller en del af en ressource er adresseret til til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressOfAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has address of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an address of an agent's place of residence, business, or employer, headquarters or offices, or an e-mail or internet address.
rdf:Description.reg:name: adressePåAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har adresse på agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressourcetil en agents bopælsadresse, forretningsadresse eller arbejdsgivers adresse og/eller en e-mail- eller internetadresse.

rdf:Description.reg:name: affiliation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has affiliation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a group with which an agent is affiliated or has been affiliated through employment, membership, cultural identity, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: tilhørsforhold
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har tilhørsforhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en gruppe, som en agent er eller har været tilknyttet via beskæftigelse, medlemskab, kulturel identitet etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: agentHistory
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has agent history
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to biographical or historical information about an agent.
rdf:Description.reg:name: agenthistorie
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har agenthistorie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til biografiske eller historiske oplysninger om en agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alsoIssuedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is also issued as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that carries the same content of a resource in a different format.
rdf:Description.reg:name: ogsåUdgivetSom
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er også udgivet som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der omfatter det samme indehold af en ressource i et andet format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternateIdentity
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternate identity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a pseudonymous or other identity assumed by an agent to an agent.
rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativIdentitet
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har alternativ identitet
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en pseudonym eller anden identitet antaget af en person til en agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativeChronologicalDesignationOfFirstIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternative chronological designation of first issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a second or subsequent system of numbering presented in the form of a date on the first issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Designation includes a year; year and month; month, day, and year. An alternative chronological designation may include a date in a different calendar.
rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativKronologiskBetegnelseForFørsteNummerEllerDelAfEnSekvens
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: alternativ kronologisk betegnelse for første nummer eller del af en sekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et andet eller efterfølgende nummereringssystem i form af en datering på første nummer eller del af nummereringssekvensen for et periodikum.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Betegnelsen omfatter et år; år og måned; måned, dag og år. En alternativ kronologisk betegnelse kan omfatte en dato i en anden kalender.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternativeChronologicalDesignationOfLastIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternative chronological designation of last issue or part of sequence

rdf:Description.reg:name: commemoration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has commemoration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource created to commemorate an earlier resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: mindemarkering
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har mindemarkering
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er skabt for at mindes en tidligere ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commemorationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commemoration of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource commemorated in a later resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: mindemarkeringAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er mindemarkering af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer n ressource til en ressource, der mindes i en senere ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that contains a set of explanatory or critical notes on a described resource
rdf:Description.reg:name: kommentarI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kommentar i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der indeholder et sæt af forklarende eller kritiske noter om en beskreven ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a set of explanatory or critical notes.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kommentarTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kommentar til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der bruges som basis for et sæt af forklarende eller kritiske kommentarer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has commentator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kommentator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har kommentator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en optrædende, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at forestå en fortolkning, analyse eller diskussion af det emne, der behandles i en optagelse, film eller andet audiovisuelt medium.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kommentatorI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kommentator i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver der bidrager til en ressource ved at give en fortolkning, analyse, eller diskussion af det emne, der behandles i en optagelse, film eller andet audiovisuelt medium til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commissioningBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has commissioning body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for commissioning a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bestillendeInstitution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har bestillende institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have bestilt en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commissioningBodyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commissioning body of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for commissioning a resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bestillendeInstitutionFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bestillende institution for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for at have bestilt en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: compiler
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has compiler
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a new resource such as a bibliography or a directory by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Revising or clarifying the content, or selecting and putting together resources or parts of resources, by one or more creators is excluded
rdf:Description.reg:name: kompilator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har kompilator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en ny ressource, fx en bibliografi eller en fortegnelse, ved at udvælge, arrangere, samle og redigere data, information etc.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Revisioner eller indholdspræciseringer, eller udvælgelse og sammensætning af værker og dele af ressourcer, af et eller flere ophav er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: compilerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is compiler of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a new resource such as a bibliography or a directory by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc., to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kompilatorAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kompilator af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt et nyt værk såsom en bibliografi eller fortegnelse ved at udvælge, arrangere, sammenlægge og redigere data, oplysninger etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: complementedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is complemented by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource paired with another resource without either resource being considered to predominate.
rdf:Description.reg:name: komplementeretAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er komplementeret af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er parret med en anden ressource, uden at én af ressourcerne betragtes som værende vigtigst.

rdf:Description.reg:name: componentOfMerger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has component of merger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that formed another agent by merging with one or more other agents to an agent.
rdf:Description.reg:name: delAfSammenlægning
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har del af sammenlægning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der har dannet en anden agent gennem sammenlægning med en eller flere andre agenter til en agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has composer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a musical resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Adaptation of another musical resource to form a distinct alteration, paraphrasing a resource or creating a resource in the general style of another composer, or creating a resource that is based on the music of another composer, is included.
rdf:Description.reg:name: komponist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: komponist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for at have skabt en musikressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Bearbejdninger af en anden musikressource for at danne en distinkt forandring ved at parafrasere en ressource eller skabe en ressource i en anden komponists typiske stil, eller skabe en ressource, der er baseret på en anden komponists musik, er omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is composer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a musical resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: komponistTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er komponist til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for at have skabt et musikværk til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordance
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of an index of all a words in a predominant resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: konkordans
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er konkordans
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der består af et indeks over alle ordene i en hovedressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordanceTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a concordance, i.e. an index of all the words in the predominant resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: konkordansTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er konkordans til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er anvendt som grundlag for en konkordans, dvs. et indeks over alle ordene i hovedressourcen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: conductor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has conductor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a musical resource by leading a performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: dirigent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har dirigent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en performer, der har bidraget til en musikressource af ved at lede en udøvende gruppe i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: conductorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is conductor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a musical resource by leading a performing group in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: dirigentAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er dirigent af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver, der bidrager til en musikalsk ressource ved at lede en udøvende gruppe i en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: configurationOfPlaybackChannels
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has configuration of playback channels
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a number of sound channels used to make a recording.
rdf:Description.reg:name: konfigurationAfAfspilningskanaler
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har konfiguration af afspilningskanaler
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et antal lydkanaler, der blev anvendt til at lave en indspilning.

rdf:Description.reg:name: consultant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has consultant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who provides consultation services, and often makes recommendations, for another agent that is represented as a creator of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: rådgiver
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har rådgiver
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der yder rådgivning, og ofte kommer med anbefalinger, til en anden agent, der er repræsenteret som ophav til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: consultantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is consultant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who provides consultation services, and often makes recommendations, for another agent that is represented as a creator of a resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: rådgiverFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er rådgiver for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der yder rådgivning, og ofte kommer med anbefalinger, til en anden agent, der er repræsenteret som ophav til en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contactInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has contact information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name, address, etc., of an organization, etc., from which a resource may be obtained.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Contact information includes the name, address, etc. of the publisher, distributor, etc. of a published resource, or of the archival repository that holds the resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kontaktoplysninger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har kontaktoplysninger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et navn, en adresse, etc. for en organisation etc. hvorfra en ressource kan fremskaffes.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Kontaktoplysninger inkluderer navn adresse, etc. på en udgiven ressources udgiver, distributør, etc., eller på det arkiv som ejer ressourcen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contained in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a larger resource of which a part is a discrete component.
rdf:Description.reg:name: indeholdtI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indeholdt i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en større ressource, som ressourcen udgør en separat del af.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is container of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is a discrete component of a larger resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: indeholderAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er indeholder af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der udgør en separat del af en større ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contentType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has content type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting a fundamental form of communication in which a content is expressed and a human sense through which it is intended to be perceived.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Content type also reflects the number of spatial dimensions and the presence or absence of movement in which content expressed in the form of an image or images is intended to be perceived.
rdf:Description.reg:name: indholdstype
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indholdstype
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en kategorisering, der afspejler den grundlæggende kommunikationsform, hvorigennem indholden ressourcekes, og den menneskelige sans, hvorigennem det er meningen, at det skal opfattes.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Hvad angår indhold, der udtrykkes i form af et eller flere billeder, afspejler indholdstype desuden antallet af rumlige dimensioner, som indholdet skal opfattes i, samt opfattelsen af tilstedeværelse eller fravær af bevægelse.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuationInPartOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continuation in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that split into two or more separate resources with new titles.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.
rdf:Description.reg:name: delvisFortsættelseAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis fortættelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er delt i to eller flere separate ressourcer med nye titler.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt for periodika.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continuation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is continued by the content of a later resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.
rdf:Description.reg:name: fortsættelseAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er fortsættelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der fortsættes af en senere ressources indhold.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvends generelt for periodika.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content continues an earlier resource under a new title.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.
rdf:Description.reg:name: erFortsatAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er fortsat af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvis indhold fortsætter en tidligere ressource med en ny titel.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt for periodika.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedInPartBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource part of whose content separated from an earlier resource to form a new resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to serials.
rdf:Description.reg:name: delvisFortsatI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis fortsat i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, hvoraf en del af indholdet er udskilt fra en tidligere ressource, så en ny ressource er dannet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt for periodika.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contributor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has contributor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Contributors include editors, translators, arrangers of music, performers, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bidragyder
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har bidragyder
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der bidrager til en ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Bidragydere omfatter bl.a. redaktører, oversættere, musikarrangører, performere.

rdf:Description.reg:name: contributorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to an expression to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bidragyderTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bidragyder til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der bidrager til en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: coordinatesOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has coordinates of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a mathematical system for identifying an area covered by the cartographic content of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: koordinaterForKartografiskIndhold
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har koordinater for kartografisk indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et matematisk system til identificering af det område, der dækkes af en ressources kartografiske indhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: copyrightDate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has copyright date
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a date associated with a claim of protection under copyright or a similar regime.
rdf:Description.reg:name: copyrightår
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har copyrightår
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et år knyttet til et krav om beskyttelse i henhold til ophavsret eller et lignende system.

rdf:Description.reg:name: costumeDesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has costume designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by designing costumes for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kostumedesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har kostumedesigner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at designe kostumer til en levende billedproduktion eller til en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller til underholdning.

rdf:Description.reg:name: costumeDesignerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is costume designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by designing costumes for a moving image production or for a musical or dramatic presentation or entertainment to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kostumedesignerTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kostumedesigner til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at designe kostumer til en levende billedproduktion eller til en musikalsk eller dramatisk præsentation eller underholdning til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: countryAssociatedWithAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has country associated with agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a country with which an agent is identified.
rdf:Description.reg:name: landKnyttetTilAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har land knyttet til agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et land som en agent forbindes med.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtGoverned
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has court governed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature.
rdf:Description.reg:name: retsinstansUnderlagt
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har retsinstans underlagt
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en retsinstans, der er underlagt retsregler, uanset hvad deres officielle art er.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtGovernedOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is court governed of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: retsinstansUnderlagt
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er retsinstans underlagt
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en retsinstans underlagt retsregler, uanset hvad deres officiele art er til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtReporter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has court reporter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by preparing a court's opinions for publication.
rdf:Description.reg:name: retsstenograf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har retsstenograf
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at klargøre en domstols afgørelser til publicering.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtReporterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is court reporter of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by preparing a court's opinions for publication to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: retsstenografI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er retsstenograf i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at klargøre en domstols afgørelser til publicering til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: coverageOfContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has coverage of content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a chronological or geographic coverage of the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: indholdsdækning
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indholdsdækning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en kronologisk eller geografisk dækning af en ressources indhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: coworker
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has co-worker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a colleague who works with or shares a task with another agent.
rdf:Description.reg:name: arbejdskollega
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har arbejdskollega
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en kollega, der arbejder sammen med eller deler opgaver med en anden agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: creator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has creator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for the creation of a resource
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Creators include agents who are jointly responsible for the creation of a resource either performing the same role, such as in a collaboration between two writers, or performing different roles, such as in a collaboration between a composer and a lyricist.
rdf:Description.reg:name: ophav
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har ophav
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for en ressources tilblivelse.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Ophav inkluderer agenter der har fælles ansvar for at have skabt en ressource, enten ved at udføre den samme rolle, som i et samarbejde mellem to forfattere, eller udføre forskellige roller, som i et samarbejde mellem fx en komponist og en sangskriver.

rdf:Description.reg:name: creatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is creator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for the creation of a resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: ophavTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er ophav til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for skabelse af en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiquedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critiqued in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that contains a critical evaluation of a described resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kritiseretI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kritiseret i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der indeholder en kritisk vurdering af en beskreven ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiqueOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critique of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as a basis for a critical evaluation.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kritikAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kritik af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource brugt som basis for en kritisk evaluering.

rdf:Description.reg:name: curator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has curator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent conceiving, aggregating, or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kurator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har kurator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent der har udtænkt, samlet og/eller arrangeret en udstilling, samling eller en anden ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: curatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is curator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent conceiving, aggregating, or organizing an exhibition, collection, or other resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: kuratorAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er kurator af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der har udtænkt, samlet og/eller arrangeret en udstilling, samling eller et andet eksemplar til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: currentOwner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has current owner
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent currently having legal possession of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: nuværendeEjer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nuværende ejer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der p.t. er i lovlig besiddelse af en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: currentOwnerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is current owner of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent currently having legal possession of a resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: nuværendeEjerAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er nuværende ejer af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der p.t. er i lovlig besiddelse af en ressource til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: custodialHistoryOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has custodial history of resource

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormatOfNotatedMusic

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormOfMusicalNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of musical notation

rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmMusikalskNotationsform
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om musikalsk notationsform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det tegnsæt og/eller symboler der anvendes for at udtrykke en ressources musikalske indhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormOfNotatedMovement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of notated movement

rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmBevægelsesnotationsform

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det sæt af tegn og/eller de symboler, der er anvendt til at udtrykke en ressources bevægelsesindhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfFormOfTactileNotation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of form of tactile notation

rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmTaktilNotationsform
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om taktil notationsform

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGeneration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of generation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a relationship between an original carrier and a carrier of a reproduction made from an original.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmGeneration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om generation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om forholdet mellem en oprindelig bærer og bæreren af en reproduktion baseret på originalen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfAudioRecording
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original audio carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a tape duplication master, a test pressing).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfDigitalResource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a digital resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a derivative master).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfMicroform
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original microform carrier and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a printing master).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfMotionPictureFilm
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a motion picture film resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a reference print).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGenerationOfVideotape
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of the relationship between an original carrier of a videotape resource and the carrier of a reproduction made from the original (e.g., a show copy).

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfGrooveCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of groove characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a groove width of an analog disc or a groove pitch of an analog cylinder.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmRillekarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om rillekarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om rillebredden på en analog disk eller rilledybden på en analog cylinder.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfIllustrativeContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of illustrative content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of content intended to illustrate a primary content of a resource.
Relates a resource to details of a presence of one or more still images that accompany the primary content of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmIllustrativtIndhold
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om illustrativt indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om indhold, der er beregnet til at illustrere et udtryks primære indhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfLayout
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an arrangement of text, images, tactile notation, etc., in a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmLayout
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om layout
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om opstilling af tekst, billeder, taktil notation etc. i en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfMount
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of mount
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a physical material used for the support or backing to which the base material of a resource has been attached.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmMontage
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om montage
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det fysiske materiale, der udgør den støtte eller bagbeklædning, som en ressources basismateriale er fastgjort på.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfPlayingSpeed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of playing speed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a speed at which an audio carrier must be operated to produce the sound intended.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmOmdrejningshastighed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om omdrejningshastighed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den hastighed, som en lydbærer skal betjenes ved for at producere den ønskede lyd.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfPolarity
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of polarity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a relationship of the colours and tones in an image to the colours and tones of the object reproduced.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmPolaritet
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om polaritet
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om forholdet mellem farver og nuancer i et billede samt farver og nuancer i den reproducerede genstand.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfPresentationFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of presentation format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a format used in the production of a projected image.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmFremvisningsformat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om fremvisningsformat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det format, der er anvendt ved fremstillingen af et projiceret billede.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfProductionMethod
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of production method
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a process used to produce a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmProduktionsmetode
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om produktionsmetode
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den proces, der er anvendt til at fremstille en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfProjectionCharacteristicOfMotionPictureFilm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of projection characteristic of motion picture film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to the projection of a motion picture film.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmProjektionskarakteristikaForFilm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om projektionskarakteristika for film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om teknisk specifikation relateret til projektion af en film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfProjectionSpeed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of projection speed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a speed at which a projected carrier must be operated to produce the moving image intended.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmProjektionshastighed
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om projektionshastighed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den hastighed, som en projiceret bærer skal betjenes ved for at producere det ønskede levende billede.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfRecordingMedium
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of recording medium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a type of medium used to record sound on an audio carrier.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmOptagemedie
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om optagemedie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det optagemedie, der er anvendt til at optage lyd på en lydbærer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfReductionRatioDesignation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of reduction ratio designation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a designation of the size of a micro-image to an original from which it was produced.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmReduktionsforholdsbetegnelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om reduktionsforholdsbetegnelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om betegnelsen for størrelse på et mikrobillede i forhold til den original, som det er fremstillet ud fra.

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of regional encoding
rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfRegionalEncoding
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a designation for one or more regions of the world for which a videodisc or video game carrier has been encoded, indicating that playback is restricted to a device configured to decode it.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmRegionalKodning
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om regional kodning
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om en kode, der identificerer den region i verden, som en videodisc er kodet til, og som forhindrer, at videodiscen bliver spillet på en afspiller solgt i en anden region.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfScript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of set of characters or symbols used to express written language content of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmSkriftstørrelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om skriftstørrelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om det sæt af tegn og/eller de symboler, der er anvendt til at udtrykke en ressources skriftlige sprogindhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfSoundCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of sound characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to the encoding of sound in a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmLydkarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om lydkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressouce til detaljer om teknisk specifikation relateret til kodning af lyd i en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfSpecialPlaybackCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of special playback characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of an equalization system, noise reduction system, etc., used in making an audio recording.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmSærligeAfspilningskarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om særlige afspilningskarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om et equalizersystem, støjdæmpningssystem etc., der er anvendt til at lave en lydoptagelse.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfTapeConfiguration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of tape configuration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a number of tracks on an audiotape.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmBåndkonfiguration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om båndkonfiguration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om antal spor på et lydbånd.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfTrackConfiguration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of track configuration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a configuration of the audio track on a sound-track film.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmLydsporskonfiguration
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om lydsporskonfiguration
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om konfiguration af lydsporet til en film med soundtrack.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfTypeOfRecording
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of type of recording
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a method used to encode audio content for playback.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmIndspilningskarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om indspilningskarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om den metode, der er anvendt til at kode lydindhold til afspilning.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfVideoCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of video characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a technical specification relating to an encoding of video images in a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmVideokarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om videokarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om teknisk specifikation relateret til kodning af videobilleder i en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: detailsOfVideoFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has details of video format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to details of a standard, etc., used to encode the analog video content of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: detaljerOmVideoformat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har detaljer om videoformat
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til detaljer om standard etc., der anvendes til kodning af en ressources analoge videoindhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digested as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that systematically and comprehensively condenses a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: sammendragetSom
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammendraget som
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der systematisk og gennemgribende komprimerer en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digest of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been digested, i.e., systematically and comprehensively condensed.
rdf:Description.reg:name: sammendragAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er sammendrag af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er et sammendrag, dvs. der er systematisk og gennemgribende komprimeret.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalFileCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital file characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a technical specification relating to a digital encoding of text, image, audio, video, and other types of data in a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalFilkarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har digitale filkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en teknisk specifikation relateret til den digitale kodning af tekst, billede, audio-, video- og andre datatyper i en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalRepresentationOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital representation of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a set of technical details relating to an encoding of geospatial information in a cartographic resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalRepræsentationAfKartografiskIndhold
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har digital repræsentation af kartografisk indhold
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et sæt af tekniske detaljer relateret til kodning af geospatiale oplysningerer i en kartografisk ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalTransfer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has digital transfer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in a digital format that results from a transfer of a resource in another digital format.
rdf:Description.reg:name: digital overførsel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har digital overførsel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource i et digitalt format, der er resultatet af en overførsel af en ressource i et andet digitalt format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalTransferOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digital transfer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource in a digital format that is transferred to another digital format.
rdf:Description.reg:name: digitalOverførselAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er digital overførsel af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource i et digitalt format, der er overført til et andet digitalt format.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dimensions
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of a carrier or a container of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: størrelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har størrelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et mål for en ressources bærer eller dens opbevaringsudstyr.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dimensionsOfMapEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions of map, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of a face of a map, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: størrelsePåKortEtcKartografi
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har størrelse på kort etc. - kartografi
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et mål for en billedside af et kort etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dimensionsOfStillImage
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dimensions of still image
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a measurement of the pictorial area of a still image.
rdf:Description.reg:name: størrelsePåFastBillede
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har størrelse på fast billede
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et mål for et fast billedes billedområde.

rdf:Description.reg:name: director
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: instruktør
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har instruktør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for ledelse af og tilsyn med en filmoptagelse, et radio- eller tv-program etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc. to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: instruktørTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er instruktør til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for ledelse af og tilsyn med en filmoptagelse, et radio- eller tv-program etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOfPhotography
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has director of photography
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent that captures images, either electronically or on film or video stock, and often selects and arranges lighting. a director of photography for a movie is also called a chief cinematographer.
rdf:Description.reg:name: filmfotografTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er filmfotograf til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der optager billeder, enten elektronisk eller på film eller video og ofte vælger og arrangerer lyssætning.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: En filmfotograf kaldes også for cheffotograf.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOfPhotographyOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is director of photography of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent that captures images, either electronically or on film or video stock, and often selects and arranges lighting. a director of photography for a movie is also called a chief cinematographer to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: filmfotografTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er filmfotograf til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent, der optager billeder, enten elektronisk eller på film eller video og ofte vælger og arrangerer lyssætning.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dissertationOrThesisInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dissertation or thesis information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement identifying an academic institution, degree, and year for which a resource was presented.
rdf:Description.reg:name: afhandlingsEllerSpecialeoplysninger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har afhandlings- eller specialeoplysninger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en oplysning der identificerer en akademisk institution, en akademisk grad og året hvor ressourcen blev forsvaret.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has distribution statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a statement identifying a place or places of distribution, distributor or distributors, and date or dates of distribution of a resource in a published form.
rdf:Description.reg:name: distibutionsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har distributionsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til oplysninger der identificerer distributionsstedet/-stederne, distributør/-er og år eller dato/-er for distribution af en ressource i publiceret form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has distributor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for distributing a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: distributør
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har distributør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der er ansvarlig for distribution af en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is distributor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for distributing a resource to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: distributørAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er distributør af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent der er ansvarlig for distribution af en manifestation til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: distributorsName
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has distributor’s name
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a name of an agent responsible for distributing a resource in a published form.
rdf:Description.reg:name: distributørnavn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har distributørnavn
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et navn på agent, der er ansvarlig for distribution af en ressource i publiceret form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: DJ
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has DJ
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who mixes recorded tracks together during a live performance or in a recording studio to appear as one continuous track.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, and mixing and assembling the multiple tracks of a recording are excluded.
rdf:Description.reg:name: djI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har dj
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der mixer indspillede spor sammen under en live optræden eller i et indspilningsstudie så de fremstår som et uafbrudt spor.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing-aktiviteter der væsentligt forandrer originalressourcens karakter og indhold og derved resulterer i en ny ressource samt mixing og sammensætning af de forskellige spor på en optagelse, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: DJOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is DJ of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a resource that incorporates a contribution of mixing recorded tracks together during a live performance or in a recording studio to appear as one continuous track.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, resulting in a new resource, and mixing and assembling the multiple tracks of a recording are excluded.
rdf:Description.reg:name: djI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er dj i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en ressource, der inkorporerer et bidrag ved at mikse indspillede spor sammen under en live-optræden eller i et indspilningsstudie så at de fremstår som et uafbrudt spor.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixingaktiviteter der fortrinsvis ændrer natur og indhold på en oprindelig ressource og derved resulterer i en ny ressource og mixe og samle in indspillings forskellige spor, er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: donor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has donor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a former owner of a resource who donated that resource to another owner.
rdf:Description.reg:name: donor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har donor

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalTheatreAdaptationOf
