rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a musical theatre resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikteaterbearbejdelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musikteaterbearbejdelse af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet til musikteater-ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource such as a motion picture, play, television program, etc., that uses a musical resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource såsom en film, et skuespil, et tv-program etc., der anvender en musikressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForMotionPicture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for motion picture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a motion picture.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikTilFilm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i en film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForRadioProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for radio program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a radio program.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikTilRadioprogram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til radioprogram
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i et radioprogram.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForTelevisionProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for television program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a television program.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikTilTvprogram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til tv-program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i et tv-program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForVideo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that uses a musical resource in a video.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikTilVideo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musik til video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der anvender en musikressource i en video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicProgrammer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has music programmer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a musical resource by using electronic audio devices or computer software to generate sounds.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The creation of a new musical resource is excluded.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikprogrammørI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har musikprogrammør
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent, der bidrager til en musikressource ved at bruge elektronisk lydudstyr og/eller computersoftware til at generere lyd.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Skabelse af en ny musikressource er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicProgrammerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music programmer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to a musical resource that incorporates a contribution of using electronic audio devices or computer software to generate sounds.
rdf:Description.reg:name: musikprogrammørI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er musikprogrammør i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en musikressource, der inkorporerer et bidrag ved at bruge elektronisk lydapparatur og/eller computersoftware til at skabe lyd.

rdf:Description.reg:name: nameOfAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters by which an agent is known.
rdf:Description.reg:name: agentsNavn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har agents navn
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et ord, tegn eller gruppe af ord og/eller tegn, som en agent er kendt under.

rdf:Description.reg:name: nameOfPlace
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has name of place
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a word, character, or group of words or characters by which a place is known.
rdf:Description.reg:name: navnPåEtSted
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har navn på et sted
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til et ord, tegn eller gruppe af ord og/eller tegn, som et sted er kendt under.

rdf:Description.reg:name: narrator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has narrator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by reading aloud or giving an account of an act, occurrence, course of events, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: fortællerIndlæser
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har fortæller/indlæser
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en optrædende, der har bidraget til en ressource ved at læse højt eller berette om en handling, en hændelse, et begivenhedsforløb etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: narratorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is narrator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by reading aloud or giving an account of an act, occurrence, course of events, etc. to a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: fortællerI
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er fortæller i
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en udøver der bidrager til en ressource ved at læse højt eller berette om en handling, en hændelse, et begivenhedsforløb, etc. til en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: natureOfContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has nature of content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a specific character of a primary content of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: indholdets art
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har indholdets art
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en specifik egenskab ved en ressources primære indhold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnCapture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on capture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information associated with the recording, filming, etc., of the content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Note on capture includes the circumstances such as a live or studio recording, the equipment used, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmOptagelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om optagelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note der giver oplysninger knyttet til optagelse, indspilning etc. af indholdet af en ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Note om optagelse omfatter forhold såsom live- eller studieoptagelse, anvendt udstyr etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnChangesInCarrierCharacteristics
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on changes in carrier characteristics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on changes in the characteristics of a carrier that occur in subsequent issues or parts of a resource issued in successive parts or between iterations of an integrating resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmÆndringerIBærerkarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ændringer i bærerkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note om ændringer i bærerens karakteristika, der optræder i efterfølgende numre eller dele af en ressource, der er udgivet i successive dele, eller mellem iterationer af en integrerende ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnChangesInContentCharacteristics
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on changes in content characteristics
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note on changes in content characteristics that occur in subsequent issues or parts of a resource issued in successive parts or between iterations of an integrating resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmÆndringerIBærerkarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ændringer i bærerkarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note om ændringer i bærerens karakteristika, der optræder i efterfølgende numre eller dele af en ressource, der er udgivet i successive dele, eller mellem iterationer af en integrerende ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnCopyrightDate
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on copyright date
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on copyright dates not recorded as part of a copyright date element.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmCopyrightÅr
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om copyrightår
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om copyrightår, der ikke er registreret som en del af copyrightangivelsen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnDimensionsOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on dimensions of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on the dimensions of a resource that is not recorded as part of a dimensions element.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmRessourcesStørrelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ressources størrelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om en ressources størrelse, der ikke er registreret som en del af størrelsesangivelsen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnDistributionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on distribution statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of distribution, distributor, or date of distribution, or information on changes in the place of distribution, distributor, or distributor’s name.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilDistributionsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til distriubutionsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der angiver detaljer om distributionssted, distributør eller distributionsår, eller oplysninger om ændringer i distributionssted, distributør eller distributørnavn.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnEditionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on edition statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on a source of an edition statement, on edition statements relating to issues, parts, etc., on changes in edition statements, or other information relating to an edition statement.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilUdgavebeskrivelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til udgavebeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om kilden til en udgavebeskrivelse, om udgavebeskrivelse relateret til numre, dele etc., om ændringer i udgavebeskrivelse eller om andre oplysninger relateret til en udgavebeskrivelse.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnExtentOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on extent of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on the extent of a resource that is not recorded as part of an extent element.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmOmfangAfRessource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om omfang af ressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om en ressources omfang, der ikke er registreret som en del af omfangsangivelsen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnFrequency
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on frequency
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on the currency of the contents, on the frequency of release of issues or parts of a serial or the frequency of updates to an integrating resource, or on changes in frequency.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmFrekvens
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om frekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om dækningsperioden, om udgivelsesfrekvensen for numre eller dele af et periodikum eller opdateringsfrekvensen for en integrerende ressource eller ændringer i frekvens.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnIdentifierForResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on identifier for resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on identifiers for a resource not recorded as part of an identifier for a resource element.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmIdentifikatorForRessourcen
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om identifikator for ressourcen
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om identifikatorer for ressourcen, der ikke fremgår af identifikatorangivelsen for ressourcen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnIssuePartOrIterationUsedAsBasisForIdentificationOfResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on issue, part, or iteration used as basis for identification of resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note identifying an issue or part of a multipart monograph or serial, or an iteration of an integrating resource that has been used as a basis for the identification of a resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmNummerDelEllerIterationAnvendtSomGrundlagForIdentifikationAfRessource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om nummer, del eller iteration, anvendt som grundlag for identifikation af ressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der identificerer et nummer eller en del af et flerbindsværk eller et periodikum, eller en iteration af en integrerende ressource, der er brugt som grundlag for identifikation af en ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnManufactureStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on manufacture statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of manufacture, manufacturer, or date of manufacture, or information on changes in place of manufacture, manufacturer, or manufacturer’s name.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilProduktionsbeskrivelsePubliceredeRessourcer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til produktionsbeskrivelse - publicerede ressourcer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om fremstillingssted, producent eller fremstillingsår, eller om ændringer i fremstillingssted, producent eller producentnavn.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnNumberingOfSerials
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on numbering of serials
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on the numbering of the first or last issue or part, on complex or irregular numbering including numbering errors, on a period covered by a volume, issue, part, etc., or on other information relating to numbering of serials.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmPeriodikanummerering
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om periodikanummerering
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om nummereringen af første og/eller sidste nummer eller del, om kompleks eller uregelmæssig nummerering (inkl. nummereringsfejl), om den periode, der dækkes af et bind, et nummer, en del etc., eller om andre oplysninger relateret til nummerering af periodika.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnProductionStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on production statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of production, producer, or date of production, or information on changes in place of production, producer, or producer’s name.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilProduktionsbeskrivelseUpubliceredeRessourcer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til produktionsbeskrivelse - upublicerede ressourcer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om produktionssted, producer eller produktionsår, eller om ændringer i produktionssted, producer eller producernavn.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnPublicationStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on publication statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing details on place of publication, publisher, or date of publication, information on changes in place of publication, publisher, or publisher’s name, or on suspension of publication.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilPubliceringsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til publiceringsbeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver detaljer om publiceringssted, udgiver eller publiceringsår eller oplysninger om ændringer i publiceringssted, udgiver eller udgivernavn, eller om ophør af publicering.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing additional information about content recorded as a resource attribute.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilRessource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til ressource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver supplerende oplysninger om indhold, der er registreret, som et attribut til udtrykket.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnResourceSpecificCarrierCharacteristic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on resource-specific carrier characteristic
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information about additional characteristics that are specific to a resource being described and are assumed not to apply to other resources exemplifying the same resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmRessourcespecifikkeIndholdskarakteristika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om ressourcespecifikke indholdskarakteristika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note om oplysninger om ekstra karakteristika, der er specifikke for en beskreven ressource og der antages ikke at være gyldige for andre ressourcer der eksemplificerere den samme ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnSeriesStatement
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on series statement
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on complex series statements, incorrect numbering within series, or changes in series statements.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilSeriebeskrivelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til seriebeskrivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om kompleks seriebetegnelse eller ukorrekt nummerering i serien, om ændringer i seriebeskrivelse eller om andre oplysninger relateret til seriebeskrivelsen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnStatementOfResponsibility
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on statement of responsibility
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on an agent not named in a statement of responsibility to whom responsibility for the creation of, or contribution to a realization of, the intellectual or artistic content of a resource has been attributed, on variant forms of names appearing in the resource, on changes in statements of responsibility, or on other details relating to a statement of responsibility.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteTilOphavsangivelse
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note til ophavsangivelse
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om en agent, der ikke er nævnt i ophavsangivelsen, men som er tillagt ansvaret for det intellektuelle eller kunstneriske indhold af værket, om variantformer af navne, der optræder i ressourcen, om ændringer i ophavsangivelser eller om andre detaljer der knytter sig til ophavsangivelsen.

rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOnTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has note on title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a note providing information on a source from which a title was taken, on the date a title was viewed, on variations in titles, on inaccuracies, deletions, etc., or other information relating to a title.
rdf:Description.reg:name: noteOmTitel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har note om titel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en note, der giver oplysninger om titlens kilde, den dato, hvor titlen blev set, titelvariationer, unøjagtigheder, sletninger etc. eller om andre oplysninger relateret til en titel.

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelization
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as novel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a novel adapted from a source resource.
rdf:Description.reg:name: bearbejdelseTilRoman
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er bearbjdet til roman
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en roman bearbejdet ud fra en oprindelig ressource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelizationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is novelization of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been adapted as a novel.
rdf:Description.reg:name: omskrivningTilRomanAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er omskrivning til roman af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en ressource, der er blevet bearbejdet som roman.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingOfPart
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering of part
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a larger resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption, and/or a chronological designation.
rdf:Description.reg:name: nummereringAfDel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering af del
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse for en del eller flere dele i et større Ressource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering af del kan omfatte et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingOfSerials
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering of serials
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation for each of the issues or parts of a serial.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption and/or a chronological designation.
rdf:Description.reg:name: nummereringAfPeriodika
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering af periodika
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en betegnelse for hvert nummer eller hver del af et periodikum.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering af omfatter et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingWithinSeries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering within series
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a series.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption and/or a chronological designation.
rdf:Description.reg:name: nummereringIndenforSerie
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering indenfor serie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse for en del eller flere dele i en serie.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering omfatter et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingWithinSubseries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering within subseries
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a part or parts within a subseries.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Numbering includes a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption and/or a chronological designation.
rdf:Description.reg:name: nummereringIndenforUnderserie
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummerering indenfor underserie
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse for en del eller flere dele i en underserie.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Nummerering omfatter et tal, et bogstav, ethvert andet tegn eller en kombination af disse med eller uden tilhørende tekst og/eller en kronologisk betegnelse.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberOfConferenceEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has number of conference, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation of a sequencing of a conference, etc., within a series of conferences, etc.
rdf:Description.reg:name: nummerPåKonferenceEtc
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har nummer på konference etc.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en sekvensbetegnelse etc. i en række af konferencer etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numericAndOrAlphabeticDesignationOfFirstIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric and/or alphabetic designation of first issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in numeric or alphabetic form presented on the first issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.
rdf:Description.reg:name: numeriskOgEllerAlfabetiskBetegnelseForFørsteNummerEllerDelafSekvens
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har numerisk og/eller alfabetisk betegnelse for første nummer eller del af sekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en betegnelse i numerisk og/eller alfabetisk form på første nummer eller del af en nummereringssekvens for et periodikum.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numericAndOrAlphabeticDesignationOfLastIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric and/or alphabetic designation of last issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a designation in numeric or alphabetic form presented on the last issue or part of a serial issued in a sequence of numbering.
rdf:Description.reg:name: numeriskOgEllerAlfabetiskBetegnelseForSidsteNummerEllerDelafSekvens
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har numerisk og/eller alfabetisk betegnelse for sidste nummer eller del af sekvens
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en betegnelse i numerisk og/eller alfabetisk form på sidste nummer eller del af en nummereringssekvens for et periodikum.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numericDesignationOfMusicalResource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric designation of musical resource
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a serial number, opus number, or thematic index number assigned to a musical resource by a composer, publisher, or a musicologist.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A numeric designation of a musical resource includes a caption such as e.g., no., op., BWV, and it may include a numeral, a letter, a word, any other character, or the combination of these.
rdf:Description.reg:name: numeriskBetegnelseForMusikressource
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har numerisk betegnelse for musikressource

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Optræden i levende billedmaterialer af faktuel karakter eller i introduktioner til levende billedmaterialer af fiktiv karakter er omfattet. Optræden på skærmen i en ikke-fremførende rolle er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: onScreenPresenterOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating an audio resource by manipulating, recombining, mixing, and reproducing previously recorded sounds.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that do not substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, and mixing recorded tracks together to appear as one continuous track are excluded.
rdf:Description.reg:name: remixer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: har remixer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en agent ansvarlig for at skabe en lydressource ved at manipulere, rekombinere, mixe og reproducere tidligere indspillede lyde.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remix-aktiviteter der ikke væsentligt ændrer natur og indhold på originalværket, og mixning af indspillede lydspor til at fremstå som et uafbrudt spor er ikke omfattet.

rdf:Description.reg:name: remixArtistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remix artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to an audio resource created by manipulating, recombining, mixing, and reproducing previously recorded sounds to a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixing activities that do not substantially change the nature and content of the original resource, and mixing recorded tracks together to appear as one continuous track are excluded.
rdf:Description.reg:name: remixerTil
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er remixer til
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en agent til en lydressource, skabt ved at manipulere, rekombinere, mixet og reproducere tidligere indspillede lyde.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Remixaktiviteter der ikke væsentligt ændrer natur og indhold på den oprindelige ressource, og miksning af indspillede lydspår til at fremstå som et uafbrudt spor ekskluderes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a later resource used in place of an earlier resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information that makes the earlier resource obsolete.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en senere ressource, der er anvendt delvist i stedet for en tidligere ressource, normalt fordi den senere ressource indeholder opdateret eller ny information, der betyder, at den tidligere ressource er forældet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Den her relation bruges generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacedInPartBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a later resource used in part in place of an earlier resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information that makes part of the earlier resource obsolete.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.
rdf:Description.reg:name: delvisErstattetAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis erstattet af

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacementInPartOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an earlier resource whose content has been partially replaced by a later resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information that makes the earlier resource obsolete.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: This relationship applies generally to single-part units, multipart monographs, and integrating resources.
rdf:Description.reg:name: delvisErstatningAf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: er delvis erstatning af
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relaterer en ressource til en tidligere ressource, hvis indhold er blevet delvist erstattet af en senere ressource, normalt fordi den senere ressource indeholder opdateret eller ny information, der betyder, at den tidligere ressource er forældet.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacementOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an earlier resource whose content has been replaced by a later resource, usually because the later resource contains updated or new information that makes the earlier resource obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: erstatningAf

rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Denne relation anvendes generelt til enkeltstående monografier, flerbindsværker og integrerende ressourcer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: restorationistOf

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for the set of technical, editorial, and intellectual procedures aimed at compensating for the degradation of a resource by bringing it back to a state as close as possible to its original condition to a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: scaleDesignation
